						               													<description>Start a cult! Perform ridiculous rituals, collect disciples and forget your morals in this fun global strategy tabletop game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Disciples is an easy-to-learn tabletop game, where you are a cult leader who collects disciples and sets up tents and temples around the world. The first player to build three temples wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You start by using your intuition to pick the 2 cards that decide your cult's name and rules. For example &amp;quot;Angels of the Gold Hive&amp;quot; or &amp;quot; Infinite Crown of Serpents&amp;quot;. There are 144 possible combinations of cults. On each turn you roll, move across the map, perform your peculiar ritual, collect new disciples, tempt fate with the Cards of Consequence and built your tents and temples in various cities around the world.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There will be lots of laughs, surprises and turns of fortune. Luck meets strategy. You may get arrested or sued for your shady behavior. If you think you're winning, you probably won't. The game takes about 30 - 60 min.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game is rated for ages 17+. Cult leaders are typically inappropriate. Fun for gamers and civilians alike.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
